"**otobo** the needed superuser privileges, run the following statement as "
"the PostgreSQL admin: ``ALTER USER otobo WITH SUPERUSER;``. Then retry "
"running http://localhost/otobo/migration.pl. After the migration, return to "
"the normal state by running ``ALTER USER otobo WITH NOSUPERUSER``."
msgstr "在这种情况下，*migration.pl*会显示 \"System was unable to complete data transfer.\"（系统无法完成数据传输）这条不太有用的信息。而 Apache 日志文件和 OTOBO 日志文件则显示了一条更有意义的信息：\"Message：ERROR: permission denied to set parameter \"session_replication_role\", SQL: 'set session_replication_role to replica;'\"。为了给数据库用户 **otobo** 所需的超级用户权限，请以 PostgreSQL 管理员身份运行以下语句：`ALTER USER otobo WITH SUPERUSER;``。然后重新运行 http://localhost/otobo/migration.pl。迁移后，运行 ``ALTER USER otobo WITH NOSUPERUSER`` 返回正常状态。"

